- Consider using templates like in the Stackoverflow rep builder to present the artist, album, link to the preview (30s), link that opens the song in Spotify, and maybe something else.

- Side nav will be Spotify's green and main will be black or dark grey.

- Search results will list all artists that match the search. This results list will be links to the individual artists. Clicking a link will pull up that artists top songs, with links to preview and play in Spotify


Function that sends AJAX call for artist search results. 
 -> Each result is a link that runs a 'topSongs' function, which runs another AJAX call and displays results to the user. 
    -> Each result will give the artist name, album the song is on, a link to the song preview and a link to the full song (will require spotify login by the user)